<h2 id='bookstores'>On-line Bookstores that stock Problem Books</h2>
<ul>
  <li><a href=
"http://www.technical.powells.portland.or.us/stacks/science.math.html">Powell's
Technical Bookstore</a><br>
  Check out listings under General/recreational.</li>
</ul>
